# machine-local state — never committed (ARCHITECTURE §3.1)
.aos/
# …except the lint selftest's planted violation, which must exist in CI checkouts
# for the overlay/state-dir check to prove itself against it
!tools/lint/selftest/fixture/.aos/
# …and golden snapshots, which record the rendered user side incl. its lockfile
!tests/golden/**/.aos/

# NOTE on MOD.md / kb-registry.yaml (the overlay family): whether users track them
# in a private fork or gitignore them is RFC-005 — deliberately NOT decided here.
# Upstream CI rejects overlay-family paths in PRs either way.

# build tooling + scratch test area
tools/node_modules/
tests/.sandbox/
